Title: Calendar Sync + (Sync Google Calendar with Outlook 2016,2013, 2010, 2007)
Description: Sync Outlook and Google Calendars (one way and two way). Metro application compatible with Windows 10 preview.
HomeWiki:
Free utility to synchronize multiple mapping of Outlook to Google calendar, Google to Outlook calendar and bidirectional with New Sync Engine!

This utility synchronizes Outlook calendar entries to a Google calendar, vice versa and both ways. Create multiple profiles to sync multiple calendars. (Outlook 2007,2010 and 2013 are supported). The Project is still under Beta with bug fixes, improvements and features coming  with every release.

  • Report issues on the Issues tab. Always attach log file, "%AppData%\CalendarSyncPlus\Log\CalSyncPlusLog.xml"
  • You can suggest improvements thru discussions or mail us
  • Access User Guide and FAQs here

ATTENTION: PLEASE READ THE FAQ HERE, TO SELECT THE APPROPRIATE SYNC DIRECTION & SETTINGS, BEFORE RUNNING THE APPLICATION

Tips & Tricks

  • Set short date time format in System Date & time settings to avoid "Outlook Entries read: 0" - Recommended format: dd-MM-yy hh:mm tt
  • Always perform clean install to avoid any error

Features

  • Tasks Sync - New
  • Office 2016 Compatibility - New
  • Multiple calendar sync
  • Manual Google Authentication
  • Add/Disconnect Multiple Google Accounts
  • Reset a selected calendar, delete all its entries (Clear)
  • Supported synchronization directions:
    • Outlook -> Google
    • Outlook <- Google
    • Outlook <-> Google
  • Synchronizes event description, attendees, reminders, availability and more
  • Synchronize calendar:
    • Days in range
    • Fixed date range
  • Set Outlook category & Event colours
  • Setup Sync Frequency
    • Interval
    • Daily
    • Weekly
  • Auto & manual synchronization
